  "backstory": {
    "title": "Vampire Overlord",
    "story": "Born beneath the crimson moon of Gearheaven, Lust was the final heir of an ancient vampire bloodline known for protecting the balance between monsters and mankind. Unlike warriors who relied only on overwhelming power, Lust believed every opponent had a weakness waiting to be discovered.\n\nHer curiosity became her greatest weapon. She studied combat patterns, learned enemy techniques, and mastered the art of prediction. Instead of carrying a traditional weapon, she transformed an enchanted giant lollipop into a legendary hunter's weapon capable of piercing defenses, controlling the battlefield, and overwhelming enemies with impossible speed.\n\nWhen her vampire clan disappeared during a forgotten conflict, Lust began traveling across Gearheaven searching for the truth. Along her journey, she discovered ancient enchantments hidden within her weapon, unlocking abilities that allowed her to bend attacks around defenses, move faster than sight, and strike before enemies could react.\n\nLust became known as the Crimson Hunger, not because of destruction, but because of her endless desire to challenge stronger opponents and uncover hidden power. To enemies, she is an unpredictable vampire who cannot be stopped. To allies, she is a fearless hunter who always finds the perfect opening."
  },

